pageProduct.name: Swisse Hemp Seed Oil 60 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Swisse Hemp Seed Oil contains raw, cold-pressed, 100% Australian Hemp Seed Oil. Providing a balanced source of Omega 3 and 6 essential fatty acids necessary for a healthy diet, Swisse Hemp Seed Oil supports nutritional wellbeing.

Swisse Hemp Seed Oil contains raw, cold-pressed, 100% Australian Hemp Seed Oil. Providing a balanced source of Omega 3 and 6 essential fatty acids necessary for a healthy diet, Swisse Hemp Seed Oil supports nutritional wellbeing.

Size: 60 Capsules

Warnings

Contains soy & sulfites.

Ingredients

HEMP Seed Oil (66%)
Gelling agents (gelatin, glycerin, purified water)
VITAMIN E (Antioxidant)

Directions

Two softgel capsules daily.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight. Do not use if cap seal is broken.
